      <h3><a href="https://www.eee-learning.com/comment/8281#comment-8281" class="permalink" rel="bookmark" hreflang="zh-hant">“陛”基本上是個比較後起的字，所以這種可能性不是很大。</a></h3>
      
        
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-comment-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h3 style="margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:7px"><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:宋体"><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-family:&quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">“</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span style="color:#3b3b3b"><a href="https://www.eee-learning.com/comment/8278#comment-8278"><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-family:&quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span style="color:#0071b3"><span style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-underline:none">陛</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span style="color:#3b3b3b">”基本上是個比較後起的字，所以這種可能性不是很大。</span></span></span></span></span></span></h3>
